sourcesContent: import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'; import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'; import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome' import { faThermometer, faWind, faDroplet } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' function ForeCastText(props) { let { current: { feelslike_c, uv, wind_kph, humidity } } = props.weather; return ( AIR CONDITION Real Feel {feelslike_c}°C Wind {wind_kph} Km/h Humidity {humidity} % UV Index {uv} ) } export default ForeCastText;
